messageBody:
On 31/10/2007, jls_nayak1983 <jls_nayak1983@...> wrote:
> May the problem be with my application, but should junit not report
> the problem why it got interrupted. Because it is not telling the
> reason of the problem, how can I debug the problem ?

Note, I also suggested that you remove everything from the code under
test that is superfluous to making the problem occur.

Start with your entire application start removing code until the only
code you have left is just that which causes the problem.

--Nat
